[["wrb.fr",null,"[null,[\"c_3acc1c26c8d1573a\",\"r_be037244e78b1f82\"],null,null,[[\"rc_dea2f073812d874a\",[\"\\u003ctool_call\\u003e{\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec_command\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"cmd\\\":\\\"git diff HEAD -- src/controllers/funnel/one_click_quantity.rs src/controllers/funnel/one_click_upsell.rs static/js/funnel-upsell.js src/views/components/conversion/_window_cleaning_side_sell.html.tera api/src/funnel/componentRegistrySchemaWindowCleaningSideSell.ts config/database/migrations/20260722010000-window-cleaning-side-sell-disclaimer/up.sql | tail -n +520 | head -n 520\\\",\\\"workdir\\\":\\\"/home/riley/spotlessbinco\\\",\\\"yield_time_ms\\\":30000,\\\"max_output_tokens\\\":36000}}\\u003c/tool_call\\u003e\\n\\u003ctool_call\\u003e{\\\"name\\\":\\\"update_goal\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\"}}\\u003c/tool_call\\u003e\\nThe `window_cleaning_side_sell` component, backend validation, client runtime, schema definitions, and migration files have been simplified to use **exact pane count only** while preserving server-authoritative one-click pricing.\\n\\n### What Changed\\n\\n1. **Frontend Template \\u0026 UI Component Editor (`src/views/components/conversion/_window_cleaning_side_sell.html.tera`, `spotless-web/ui/src/components/admin/funnel/ComponentEditor/forms/WindowCleaningSideSellForm.tsx`)**:\\n   - Removed house size option choices (`Small`, `Medium`, `Large`, `Extra Large`) and choice button selector rendering.\\n   - Simplified copy and input state to collect pane count ($1\\\\text{--}200$) directly.\\n\\n2. **Client Up-Sell JS (`static/js/funnel-upsell.js`)**:\\n   - Removed `card.dataset.houseSize` dependency and request payload mapping.\\n   - Client sends `quantity: Number.parseInt(card.dataset.paneCount, 10)` directly to the one-click endpoint.\\n\\n3. **Server Validation \\u0026 Controller Logic (`src/controllers/funnel/one_click_quantity.rs`, `src/controllers/funnel/one_click_upsell.rs`)**:\\n   - Removed house size selection checking (`selection.ok_or(...)` and allowed array matching).\\n   - Validates that the offer uses per-pane unit pricing and verifies that `quantity` is within $1\\\\text{--}200$.\\n   - Calculates the final total server-side (`unit_amount_cents * quantity`) to guarantee server authority on price.\\n\\n4. **Component Schema, Descriptions\"],null,null,null,null,null,null,[1],\"en\",null,null,[null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[]],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,[]]],[\"Lavon, TX, USA\",\"SWML_DESCRIPTION_FROM_YOUR_INTERNET_ADDRESS\",false,null,\"//www.google.com/maps/vt/data\\u003dkxGNWLMWtoBa-79WrzrBHe0msgrD3u6d6Yqnr2FIjayFJXag_tNga-2qoxT2Xmw6MBTWZQFb19F8Lis3Oi5QmnUV6k7yx0BBUBLBdHg-rxuZKxRruEKBk4l2xi9nIyZGMVLzymnJW0cP-Yf1wALsNUPBWZH7yFfJo1MszhNHn4xfusgUM8gOuvo68iHstoCS\"],null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,false,null,null,null,null,\"en\",null,null,null,true,null,null,[[[[null,[null,0,\"\\u003ctool_call\\u003e{\\\"name\\\":\\\"exec_command\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"cmd\\\":\\\"git diff HEAD -- src/controllers/funnel/one_click_quantity.rs src/controllers/funnel/one_click_upsell.rs static/js/funnel-upsell.js src/views/components/conversion/_window_cleaning_side_sell.html.tera api/src/funnel/componentRegistrySchemaWindowCleaningSideSell.ts config/database/migrations/20260722010000-window-cleaning-side-sell-disclaimer/up.sql | tail -n +520 | head -n 520\\\",\\\"workdir\\\":\\\"/home/riley/spotlessbinco\\\",\\\"yield_time_ms\\\":30000,\\\"max_output_tokens\\\":36000}}\\u003c/tool_call\\u003e\\n\\u003ctool_call\\u003e{\\\"name\\\":\\\"update_goal\\\",\\\"arguments\\\":{\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\"}}\\u003c/tool_call\\u003e\\nThe window_cleaning_side_sell component, backend validation, client runtime, schema definitions, and migration files have been simplified to use exact pane count only while preserving server-authoritative one-click pricing.\",[[619,644,[[null,null,null,nul